## Ethical Use Addendum

This software is intended solely for authorized security testing purposes:

1. Penetration testing with explicit written authorization
2. Red team exercises with signed rules of engagement
3. Security research in controlled, isolated environments
4. CTF competitions and educational contexts

The authors and contributors are not responsible for any misuse of this
software. Users must ensure they have proper authorization before using
this tool against any systems they do not own.
